SOFTWARE REQUIREMENT SPECIFICATION (SRS)

1. Introduction  
This document defines the functional and non-functional requirements of the Sales Performance Analysis System.

2. Functional Requirements  
- Upload sales data from Excel  
- Analyze sales by region and product  
- Identify low-performing regions  
- Display results in dashboard  
- Export reports  
- Provide business recommendations  

3. Non-Functional Requirements  
- Easy to use UI  
- Fast processing  
- Secure data handling  
- Compatible with Windows  
- Scalable design  

4. System Architecture  
- Frontend: React  
- Backend: Python  
- Data Source: Excel  
- Dashboard: Power BI  

5. Hardware Requirements  
- Minimum 4GB RAM  
- Dual Core Processor  
- 10GB Free Storage  

6. Software Requirements  
- VS Code  
- Python 3.x  
- Power BI  
- Node.js  
- MS Excel  

7. Constraints  
- Limited dataset  
- Standalone system  
- No real-time data  
